title: "Good on Paper" theater review: A slight comedy by Creede Repertory at Arvada
text:
Published By: Denver Post Entertainment - Today 
Paper-thin but enjoyable as a fairy tale, Creede Repertory Theatre's "Good on Paper" at the Arvada Center requires a suspension of disbelief...
